title: James Luther Dickinson - Killers From Space (2007)
description:
James Luther Dickinson - Killers From Space (2007)

James Luther Dickinson (vocals, 12-string guitar, harp, keyboards) 
Ed Finney, Jimbo Mathus, Luther Dickinson (guitar)
Paul Taylor (electric guitar, chimes)
Chris Scruggs (steel guitar, dobro)
Greg Spradlin (baritone guitar, background vocals)
'T-Bone' Tommy Burroughs (mandolin, fiddle)
Jonathan Kirkscey (cello)
Johnny Reno (tenor saxophone)
Cody Dickinson (drums)

"Acolyte of bluesmen Furry Lewis and Sleepy John Estes, sideman of Dylan and the Rolling Stones, producer of Big Star, the Replacements and Screamin' Jay Hawkins, world-class song bag, down-home bon vivant and fond father of several North Mississippi Allstars, Jim Dickinson is a legend. 

  01. Texas Me 
  02. Dirty On Yo, Mama 
  03. Nature Boy 
  04. Eloise 
  05. You Better Rock Me Baby 
  06. Lonely Nights 
  07. I Need You 
  08. Roly Poly 
  09. Morning After the Night Before 
  10. No, No Never Again 
  11. I Was a Champion 
  12. Sweet Peace Within 

  If you like the music, buy it!
